    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2007-05-22</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2007-06-27T19:31:47Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Renewable Schools Energy Act of 2007 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a tax credit for investment in qualified renewable school energy bonds. Defines &quot;qualified renewable school energy bond&quot; as a bond with a 20-year term, 95% of the proceeds of which are used for the purchase and installation of renewable energy products for public school and school district administrative buildings in states with a specified percentage of population growth. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
